<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ideedf6fc9-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s1636e"><num value="1636e">§ 1636e.</num><heading> Voluntary reporting</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall encourage voluntary reporting by packers (as defined in <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s191">section 191 of this title</ref>) to which the mandatory reporting requirements of this subchapter do not apply.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ideedf6fca-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1946-08-14/ch966">Aug. 14, 1946, ch. 966</ref>, title II, § 256, as added <ref href="/us/pl/106/78/tIX/s911/2">Pub. L. 106–78, title IX, § 911(2)</ref>, <date date="1999-10-22">Oct. 22, 1999</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/113/1204">113 Stat. 1204</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
